- Cybersecurity → hooded figure at multiple monitors with scrolling terminal code, dim blue atmosphere
- GPU/hardware launch → engineer holding chip up, ${subjectName} logo visible on packaging behind them
- AI framework release → developer at desk with VS Code open, code on screen, coffee mug nearby
- Funding/deal → handshake in glass office, city skyline behind
- Robot/automation → humanoid robot or robotic arm in modern lab

